Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:13.84,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.60,0:08:15.58,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Pepř...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.78,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ale no tak, Margarito!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.27,0:08:22.26,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Můžete jí přestat učit blbosti? Docela mi to ztěžuje život...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.33,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,A máš tam nos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:30.49,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hele...
