Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.23,0:09:16.92,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nemusíš se takhle nutit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:19.66,dialog-raw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
